sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant C as Client
    participant G as JwtAuthGuard
    participant Ctl as OrdersController.list
    participant Svc as OrdersService
    participant DB as Prisma / Postgres
    C->>G: GET /orders (Bearer JWT)
    G->>Ctl: req.user.id = exhibitorId
    Ctl->>Svc: listOrders(exhibitorId, query)
    Svc->>DB: resolve companyId, then order.findMany({ company_id, deleted_at:null })
    DB-->>Svc: rows
    Svc->>Svc: derive payment_status / is_overdue / can_pay + buildOrderShows
    Svc-->>Ctl: { data[], meta, isEmpty }
    Ctl-->>C: 200 OrderListResponseDto
